---
title: "US38 — Customise plan parameters"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>PlanDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>RegeneratePlan
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>FitnessPlan · PlannedWorkout
  A->>B: change duration / frequency / preferences
  B->>C: generate() (regenerate)
  C->>E: suggestPlan() (revised options)
  E-->>C: AI plan draft
  C->>E: insertPlan(regenerated_count + 1) + setActivePlan(...)
  E-->>C: FitnessPlan + PlannedWorkouts (updated)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (plan persisted)
  B-->>A: plan reflects custom parameters
  note over E: suggestPlan via AiGateway → suggest-plan Edge Function —<br/>persisted via PlanGateway (RLS). Free capped at 1 regenerate
